    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We experienced regeneration"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When we opened to this living One."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We were born again; another life came in."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now it floods us till we’re full of Him."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He within us is the living Spirit"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In our spirit, flowing out of it"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Into all our heart, transforming every part"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By the life which He Himself imparts."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now He must have our cooperation."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We must set our mind upon the Son."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We must turn away from all that leads astray,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Till our mind is set on Him each day."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, our human spirit now contains You."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Still Your purpose in us You would do;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If our wandering mind would leave old thoughts behind,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then Your life and peace in it we’ll find."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, we would our every thought be captured"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By the rich enjoyment in Your Word."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In it we’re supplied, our mind there will abide,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Till our thoughts are wholly sanctified."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Let’s keep practicing the application"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of this life by minding just the Son."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Praise Him for the way to live by Him today!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, on You our minds will ever stay."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    }
